{"tid":1949941,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英媒報導英國因不滿中國隱匿疫情 或以排除華為參與5G建設作報復","createTime":"2020-03-30T04:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T06:10:32.000Z","uid":28765,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aadcec615ba17614b5996347a78dcb659d7689e4","tid":1949941,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"（中央社倫敦29日綜合外電報導）美國雜誌「財經內幕」（Business Insider）今天引述英國「週日郵報」報導，英國強生政府非常不滿中國對武漢肺炎疫情的處理，一旦危機結束，英方勢必重新檢討雙方關係。<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，由於強生（Boris Johnson）政府非常不滿中國，以致可能撤銷先前決定，不再允許中國電信巨擘華為（Huawei）開發英國5G網絡。<br />\n<br />\n「週日郵報」（Mail on Sunday）指出，英國官員認為中國散布有關國內疫情嚴重程度的不實消息。官員也認為，中國試圖藉著協助其他抗疫的國家來擴大經濟實力。<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，科學家提醒強生，中國可能低報確診人數「15至40倍」。<br />\n<br />\n這篇報導發出時，中國通報8萬1439例確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n一位官員表示：「這件事情過後，外交政策將會重新規劃。」第2位不具名官員說，這場危機結束之後，「一定會檢討雙方關係」；另一人則說，「憤怒直達最高層」。<br />\n<br />\n「週日郵報」指出，由於強生政府非常不滿中國對危機的處理，以致強生可能不再允許華為開發英國5G。<br />\n<br />\n強生決定在開發英國網路基礎建設上給予華為有限但重要的角色，惹惱盟友美國總統川普。據說川普上月和強生通電話時對此表達不滿，之後「勃然大怒地」掛上電話。<br />\n<br />\n「週日郵報」引述一位內閣官員表示：「我們不能袖手旁觀，讓中國隱匿的意圖毀了世界的經濟，然後回過頭來，好像什麼都沒發生過。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們不只任由華為這樣的公司進入我國經濟，也讓華為在我國的基礎建設扮演重要角色。」<br />\n<br />\n「這需要盡快檢討，仰賴中國供應鏈、有戰略重要性的基礎建設，也應該如此。」（譯者：鄭詩韻/核稿：嚴思祺）1090330<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202003300040.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202003300040.aspx&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYq%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=4cbd5044\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202003300040.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"7a2815ca008b2e15842edc8adda9c788126eecd5","tid":1949941,"uid":255637,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係要到奶左野先知驚"},{"pid":"a6f7230b7ec871afe90e076389f0fb40541164e8","tid":1949941,"uid":14816,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7a2815ca008b2e15842edc8adda9c788126eecd5","tid":1949941,"uid":255637,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:08:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係要到奶左野先知驚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:12:47.000Z","msg":"中個武肺識驚<br />\n都好過賣撚埋個國家走先識驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40be3aaecdab0ec1ac26865a34583424634506e6","tid":1949941,"uid":92194,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:16:01.000Z","msg":"留名日落繼續奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb86b85bc77b9a723d376eb3072c4123bb3d8636","tid":1949941,"uid":260271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:17:29.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入"},{"pid":"b3f1ff29a92d1c508a6efb67ad7d4f0a62405655","tid":1949941,"uid":321977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:19:52.000Z","msg":"支那附屬國而家先識醒？等睇事頭婆中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6f3c1e1c2e8f9975831573d6fd8f56f54daaeb","tid":1949941,"uid":151903,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:21:28.000Z","msg":"首相嬲豬了"},{"pid":"784c780907633c8336321c27f5583b1c2e4e13c3","tid":1949941,"uid":40588,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xxANXXB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxxANXXB.png&h=36eb9768&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddc2c1c64b058dc8498ec920c9811abbf81f323b","tid":1949941,"uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"要王室同政府高官出事先醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c16cda0b778fc55a10a145c8283307a5307b4d","tid":1949941,"uid":189328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:09:19.000Z","msg":"佢之前有同美國係度嘈用華為問題， 仲要脫埋歐， 佢見而家 形勢扮下嘢啫 遲啲又可能 用返5g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21012c28816b488ac9068385dac40ad2271fd08e","tid":1949941,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"聽住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}